Grosseteste, Bischofs von Lincoln</em> (Beitr&auml;ge zur geschichte
der philosophie des mittelalters 9), M&uuml;nster: Aschendorff
Verlag.</p>

<p class="bibnote">
[This text includes the standard edition of Grosseteste&rsquo;s
philosophical treatises, too. As noted above, Baur&rsquo;s edition is
unreliable and new editions of Grosseteste&rsquo;s works supersede it
(see below.)]</p> </li>

<li>

<p class="nobottommargin">
Dales, Richard C. (ed.), 1963b, &ldquo;Robert Grosseteste&rsquo;s
