Lincolniensis commentarius in viii libros Physicorum Aristotelis</em>,
Boulder, CO: University of Colorado Press.</p>

<p class="bibnote">
[Unfortunately, a flawed edition of this important work that must be
used with great caution. A new edition is in preparation by N. Lewis
and P. King.]</p> </li>

