<em>Ecclesiasticus</em>, ch. 43, vv. 1&ndash;5&rdquo;, <em>Recherches
de th&eacute;ologie ancienne et m&eacute;di&eacute;vale</em>, 41:
38&ndash;91; reprinted in
 <a href="#McEvoy1994">McEvoy 1994</a>.</p>
 
<p class="bibnote">
[This commentary is also known as <em>De operationibus
solis</em>.]</p> </li>

<li>

<p class="nobottommargin">
Lewis, Neil Timothy (ed.), 2017, <em>Robert Grossteste &ldquo;On Free
Decision&rdquo;</em> (Auctores Britannici Medii Aevi 29), Oxford/New
York: Published for the British Academy by Oxford University
Press.</p>

<p class="bibnote">
[Editions and English translation of the two recensions of
Grosseteste&rsquo;s <em>De libero arbitrio</em>. It supersede the
editions in
 <a href="#Baur1912">Baur 1912</a>.]</p>
 </li>
</ul>

