<h3 id="PriTexEngTra">D. Primary Texts in English Translation</h3>

<h4>D.1 Scientific treatises</h4>

<ul class="hanging">

<li>

<p class="nobottommargin">
Crombie, A. C., 1955, &ldquo;Grosseteste&rsquo;s Position in the
History of Science&rdquo;, in <em>Robert Grosseteste: Scholar and
Bishop</em>, Daniel A. Callus (ed.), Oxford: Clarendon Press,
98&ndash;120.</p>

<p class="bibnote">
[Contains a translation of <em>De calore solis</em> (116&ndash;120).
The authenticity of this work is challenged in
 <a href="#Panti2013b">Panti 2013b</a>.]</p>
 </li>

<li>

<p class="nobottommargin">
Dales, Richard C., 1966, &ldquo;The Text of Robert Grosseteste&rsquo;s
