<em>A Source Book in Medieval Science</em>, Edward Grant (ed.),
Cambridge, MA: Harvard University Press, 640&ndash;644; and in
 <a href="#Dales1973">Dales 1973</a>.
 doi:10.1086/350162</p>

<p class="bibnote">
[The authenticity of this work is challenged in
 <a href="#Dales1977">Dales 1977</a>,
 <a href="#Southern1986">Southern 1986</a>, and
 <a href="#Panti2013b">Panti 2013b</a>.]</p>
 </li>

<li id="Dales1973">

