&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1973, <em>The Scientific Achievement of the
Middle Ages</em>, Philadelphia, PA: University of Pennsylvania
Press.</p>

<p class="bibnote">
[Contains translations of <em>De impressionibus elementorum</em>,
<em>De calore solis</em> and <em>De fluxu et refluxu maris</em>. The
authenticity of the last work is challenged in
 <a href="#Dales1977">Dales 1977</a>,
 <a href="#Southern1986">Southern 1986</a>, and
 <a href="#Panti2013b">Panti 2013b</a>.
 Panti 2013b also challenges the authenticity of <em>De calore
solis</em>]</p> </li>

<li>

<p class="nobottommargin">
