<div id="other-internet-resources">

<h2 id="Oth">Other Internet Resources</h2>

<ul>

<li>The
 <a href="https://grossetestesociety.org" target="other">International Robert Grosseteste Society</a>,
 a learned society for the study of Robert Grosseteste. Its website
offers insights on Grosseteste&rsquo;s thought as well as updates on
new studies and events.</li>

<li>The
 <a href="https://rogerbaconresearchsociety.com/" target="other">Roger Bacon Research Society</a>,
 a learned society dedicated to the study of Roger Bacon. Its website
provides a comprehensive bibliography, including numerous studies
related to Grosseteste.</li>
</ul>
</div>

